name: Insert Title
description:
A game for the Wowie! Jam 2.0.

I started development on saturday and finished on sunday, I feel like the game could be a lot better with more time, having better sprites, and better polished code. I could barely expand on the platformer section, that played more with "glitched mechanics". 

The game is called "Insert Title" because is just a mesh and is also the fist game I publish, I hope you like it.
